            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.059,
                0.156,
                0.243,
                0.184
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\(\\left(0, \\frac{1}{4}\\right)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.192,
                0.711,
                0.224
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\(F^{\\prime}(x) = 2 - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} = 0\\) 得 \\(x = \\frac{1}{4}\\)，当 \\(0 < x < \\frac{1}{4}\\) 时 \\(F^{\\prime}(x) < 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.234,
                0.372,
                0.26
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(F(x)\\) 的单调减区间为 \\(\\left(0, \\frac{1}{4}\\right)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.059,
                0.27,
                0.314,
                0.302
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\left\\{0, \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{5}, \\frac{\\sqrt{15}}{5}\\right\\}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.308,
                0.505,
                0.323
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 旋转曲面方程为 \\(\\Sigma:3x^{2} + 2y^{2} + 3z^{2} = 12\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.089,
                0.331,
                0.523,
                0.347
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "法向量为 \\(n = \\{6x,4y,6z\\}_{(0,\\sqrt{3},\\sqrt{2})} = \\{0,4\\sqrt{3},6\\sqrt{2}\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.356,
                0.459,
                0.385
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所求的单位法向量为 \\(n^0 = \\left\\{0, \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{5}, \\frac{\\sqrt{15}}{5}\\right\\}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.396,
                0.203,
                0.424
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\(\\frac{2\\pi}{3}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.433,
                0.507,
                0.46
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(b_{3} = \\frac{1}{\\pi}\\int_{-\\pi}^{\\pi}f(x)\\sin 3x\\mathrm{d}x = 2\\int_{0}^{\\pi}x\\sin 3x\\mathrm{d}x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.174,
                0.469,
                0.705,
                0.498
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= - \\frac {2}{3} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} x \\mathrm {d} (\\cos 3 x) = - \\frac {2}{3} x \\cos 3 x \\left| _ {0} ^ {\\pi} + \\frac {2}{3} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\cos 3 x \\mathrm {d} x = \\frac {2 \\pi}{3}. \\right.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.061,
                0.507,
                0.291,
                0.538
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(4)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.545,
                0.743,
                0.574
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\operatorname{grad} u = \\left\\{\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z}\\right\\} = \\left\\{\\frac{x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right\\},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.583,
                0.74,
                0.612
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(\\operatorname{div}(\\mathbf{grad} u) = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(\\frac{x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right) + \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial y}\\left(\\frac{y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right) + \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial z}\\left(\\frac{z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.218,
                0.619,
                0.692,
                0.689
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} = \\frac {y ^ {2} + z ^ {2} - x ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} + \\frac {x ^ {2} + z ^ {2} - y ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} + \\frac {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} - z ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} \\\\ = \\frac {1}{x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.695,
                0.464,
                0.71
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(5)【答案】 \\(X = k(1,1,\\dots ,1)^{\\mathrm{T}}(k\\) 为任意常数)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.716,
                0.743,
                0.815
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(r(\\mathbf{A}) = n - 1\\) ，所以 \\(\\mathbf{AX} = \\mathbf{0}\\) 的基础解系含一个线性无关的解向量，又因为 \\(\\mathbf{A}\\left[ \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ 1\\\\ \\vdots \\\\ 1 \\end{array} \\right] = \\mathbf{0}\\) ，所以 \\(\\mathbf{AX} = \\mathbf{0}\\) 的通解为 \\(\\mathbf{X} = k(1,1,\\dots ,1)^{\\mathrm{T}}(k\\) 为任意常数）."
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.821,
                0.15,
                0.836
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.842,
                0.208,
                0.857
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.863,
                0.66,
                0.891
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 由 \\(\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{x^3} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\cos x\\cdot\\sin(\\sin^2x)}{3x^2} = \\frac{1}{3}\\) 得 \\(f(x)\\sim \\frac{1}{3} x^{3}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.9,
                0.659,
                0.915
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又 \\(g(x)\\sim x^3\\) ，故 \\(f(x)\\) 是 \\(g(x)\\) 的同阶但非等价的无穷小，应选(B)."
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.068,
                0.212,
                0.083
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（2）【答案】 （A）."
        },
        {
