                0.088,
                0.648,
                0.105
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 双纽线 \\((x^{2} + y^{2})^{2} = x^{2} - y^{2}\\) 的极坐标方程为 \\(r^2 = \\cos 2\\theta\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.111,
                0.38,
                0.126
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由对称性得双纽线所围成的面积为"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.346,
                0.131,
                0.684,
                0.162
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nA = 4 \\times \\frac {1}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{4}} \\cos 2 \\theta d \\theta = 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{4}} \\cos 2 \\theta d \\theta ,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.17,
                0.174,
                0.184
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.191,
                0.21,
                0.206
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.212,
                0.486,
                0.228
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 直线 \\(L_{1}\\) 的方向向量为 \\(s_1 = \\{1, - 2,1\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.234,
                0.65,
                0.25
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "直线 \\(L_{2}\\) 的方向向量为 \\(\\pmb{s}_2 = \\{1, - 1,0\\} \\times \\{0,2,1\\} = \\{-1, - 1,2\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.256,
                0.687,
                0.289
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "设两直线的夹角为 \\(\\theta\\)，由 \\(\\cos \\theta = \\frac{|s_1 \\cdot s_2|}{|s_1| \\cdot |s_2|} = \\frac{1}{2}\\) 得 \\(\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{3}\\)，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.294,
                0.208,
                0.309
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 （B）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.316,
                0.663,
                0.332
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】令 \\(P(x,y) = [f(x) - \\mathrm{e}^x ]\\sin y\\) ， \\(Q(x,y) = -f(x)\\cos y,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.338,
                0.633,
                0.368
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(\\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y}\\) 得 \\(f^{\\prime}(x) + f(x) - \\mathrm{e}^{x} = 0\\) ，即 \\(f^{\\prime}(x) + f(x) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.375,
                0.585,
                0.405
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "解得 \\(f(x) = \\left[\\int \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{\\int \\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right]\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int \\mathrm{d}x} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + C\\right)\\mathrm{e}^{-x},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.413,
                0.585,
                0.442
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由 \\(f(0) = 0\\) 得 \\(C = -\\frac{1}{2}\\)，故 \\(f(x) = \\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - \\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{2}\\)，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.45,
                0.208,
                0.465
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.471,
                0.724,
                0.487
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】由 \\( PQ = O \\) 得 \\( r(P) + r(Q) \\leqslant 3 \\)，当 \\( t \\neq 6 \\) 时 \\( r(Q) = 2 \\)，则 \\( r(P) \\leqslant 1 \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.492,
                0.546,
                0.507
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "再由 \\(\\pmb{P}\\) 为非零矩阵得 \\(r(P)\\geqslant 1\\) ，故 \\(r(P) = 1\\) ，应选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.514,
                0.094,
                0.529
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "三、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.061,
                0.536,
                0.857,
                0.577
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 \\(\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}}\\right)^{x} = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left\\{\\left[1 + \\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}} - 1\\right)\\right]^{\\frac{1}{\\sin{\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos{\\frac{1}{x}} - 1}}\\right\\} x\\cdot \\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}} - 1\\right)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.342,
                0.584,
                0.669,
                0.624
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n= \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow \\infty} \\frac {\\sin \\frac {2}{x} + \\cos \\frac {1}{x} - 1}{\\frac {1}{x}}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\lim  _ {t \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin 2 t + \\cos t - 1}{t}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.63,
                0.215,
                0.645
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（2）【解】 方法一"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.651,
                0.785,
                0.687
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\int \\frac {x \\mathrm {e} ^ {x}}{\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}} \\mathrm {d} x = \\int \\frac {x \\mathrm {d} (\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1)}{\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}} = 2 \\int x \\mathrm {d} (\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}) = 2 x \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - 2 \\int \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} \\mathrm {d} x,\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.696,
                0.411,
                0.713
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = t\\) ，即 \\(x = \\ln (1 + t^{2})\\) ，则"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.72,
                0.687,
                0.777
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int \\sqrt {e ^ {x} - 1} d x = \\int t \\cdot \\frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t = 2 \\int \\left(1 - \\frac {1}{1 + t ^ {2}}\\right) d t = 2 t - 2 \\arctan t + C \\\\ = 2 \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - 2 \\arctan \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + C, \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.784,
                0.606,
                0.817
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\int \\frac{x\\mathrm{e}^x}{\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1}}\\mathrm{d}x = (2x - 4)\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} +4\\arctan \\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} +C.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.826,
                0.603,
                0.855
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二 令 \\(\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = t\\) ，则 \\(x = \\ln (1 + t^{2}),\\mathrm{d}x = \\frac{2t}{1 + t^{2}}\\mathrm{d}t,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.862,
                0.593,
                0.934
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int \\frac {x e ^ {x}}{\\sqrt {e ^ {x} - 1}} d x = \\int \\frac {\\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) \\cdot (1 + t ^ {2})}{t} \\cdot \\frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t \\\\ = 2 \\int \\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) d t = 2 t \\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) - 2 \\int \\frac {t \\cdot 2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.212,
                0.073,
                0.585,
                0.109
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} = 2 t \\ln \\left(1 + t ^ {2}\\right) - 4 t + 4 \\arctan t + C \\\\ = (2 x - 4) \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + 4 \\arctan \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + C. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.117,
                0.556,
                0.145
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【解】 将方程 \\(x^{2}y^{\\prime} + xy = y^{2}\\) 化为 \\(y^\\prime +\\frac{1}{x} y = \\frac{1}{x^2} y^2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.153,
                0.374,
                0.182
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "令 \\(u = y^{-1}\\) ，则 \\(\\frac{\\mathrm{d}u}{\\mathrm{d}x} -\\frac{1}{x} u = -\\frac{1}{x^2},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.188,
                0.777,
                0.22
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "解得 \\(u = \\left[\\int \\left(-\\frac{1}{x^2}\\right)\\mathrm{e}^{\\int -\\frac{1}{x}\\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right]\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -\\frac{1}{x}\\mathrm{d}x} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2x^2} +C\\right)x\\) ，即 \\(\\frac{1}{y} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2x^2} +C\\right)x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.227,
                0.574,
                0.256
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(y(1) = 1\\) 得 \\(C = \\frac{1}{2}\\)，故满足条件的特解为 \\(y = \\frac{2x}{1 + x^2}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.264,
                0.549,
                0.282
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、【解】 由 \\(\\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} = \\sqrt{2 - x^2 - y^2}\\) 得 \\(x^{2} + y^{2} = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.288,
                0.835,
                0.326
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "曲面 \\(\\Sigma\\) 所围成的几何体 \\(\\Omega = \\{(x, y, z) \\mid x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 1, \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} \\leqslant z \\leqslant \\sqrt{2 - x^2 - y^2}\\}\\), 由高斯公式得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.332,
                0.83,
                0.439
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\iint_ {z} 2 x z \\mathrm {d} y \\mathrm {d} z + y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x - z ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iiint_ {\\Omega} (2 z + z - 2 z) \\mathrm {d} v = \\iiint_ {\\Omega} z \\mathrm {d} v \\\\ = \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} d x d y \\int_ {\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}}} ^ {\\sqrt {2 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}}} z d z = \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} (1 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}) d x d y \\\\ = \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} d \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {1} (r - r ^ {3}) d r = \\frac {\\pi}{2}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.449,
                0.415,
                0.482
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】 令 \\(S(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}(n^{2} - n + 1)x^{n}\\)，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.088,
                0.485,
                0.628,
                0.518
            ],
            "angle": 0,
